Author: bir_die
Text: I mean, without her directly telling you it could be a whole handful of things.   She could just have a specialized diet and is deep into nutrition. Plus, you probably don’t see 100% of what she eats in an entire day. And dark head hair does not equal dark body hair. Plenty of people end up with light peach fuzz rather than the thick black hair others have.   Tbh, I’d just leave it alone. I don’t know about you, but ED or not, I’d be pretty upset if my roommate tried to confront me about having one.
